data.description:
SELLER OFFERING $5,000.00 IN CONCESSIONS!!!! VERY MOTIVATED SELLER!!!! PRICE REDUCTION!!!!!
Welcome Home. This very clean and well-maintained townhome in a great community with great access to TX-121 and the Tollway. 3-2.5-2 gem in the Cascades! This home has siltstone countertops, under mount sink, C-tiles in kitchen, Ceiling Fans, monitored security and lots of natural light. Centrally located to many restaurants, music venues, shopping, Grandscape, The Star, Lava Cantina, Lake Lewisville and so much more.
PREFERRED LENDER: RHL Lending, www.rhllending.com. If buyer uses RHL Lending, they are eligible for a credit of up to 1% of the purchase price of the home to buy down their interest rate.
